   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To the archephodos of Psobthis in the middle toparchy. Send Pammounis, seller cultivator (?) of Sarapi- . . . who was accused by Apion, the collector of public taxes . . . send with a guard. Choiak [ ] . . ."</ab>
